    public abstract class FlinkAbstractParDoWrapper<IN,OUTDF,OUTFL>
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.RichFlatMapFunction<WindowedValue<IN>,WindowedValue<OUTFL>>
    An abstract class that encapsulates the common code of the the ParDo.Bound and ParDo.BoundMulti wrappers. See the FlinkParDoBoundWrapper and FlinkParDoBoundMultiWrapper for the actual wrappers of the aforementioned transformations.
